Iteration 14 - worker lifecycle / failover validation
Date: 2026-05-21 (Asia/Taipei)

Root cause fixed:
- services/nodepool/internal/service/worker_service.go
- ListWorkers(includeOffline=true) was auto-reactivating OFFLINE workers when heartbeat age was fresh.
- This caused failed nodes to remain/return ACTIVE in UI/API even after probe-based offline marking.

Fix:
- Preserve explicit OFFLINE state in ListWorkers; only empty status is normalized to ACTIVE.

Build and restart:
- go build -o services/nodepool/nodepool.exe ./services/nodepool/cmd/server
- go build -o services/worker/worker.exe ./services/worker/cmd/server
- powershell -ExecutionPolicy Bypass -File scripts/start_stable_stack.ps1

